author: GameSpot
description:
Plus, there are a bunch of hot people with superpowers in this story, and Dispatch lets you unashamedly flirt with two of them. A truly perfect experience would have let us smooch 'em all, obviously, but of the two options that we did get? Their romantic arcs are fun, flirty, and deeply rewarding to watch play out (in drastically different ways too!), and a great incentive to play through Dispatch's fantastic story at least twice.

title: Dispatch: GameSpot's Top 10 Games Of 2025
